<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 kẖbạ̉t klạmk fy qlby lkylạ ạ̉kẖṭỷ ạ̹lyk
 mbạrk ạ̉nt yạ rby ʿlmny frạỷḍk
 bm ạ̉zky ṭryqy wsẖbạby yqwdny ạ̹ly̱ ạlhwạn
 klạmk sndy rfyqy yḥfẓ drby fy kl ận
 bṭryq sẖhạdạtk frḥt ḥsbt kl ạ̉ḥkạmk
 bfrạỷḍk ạ̉nạ tldẖdẖt lạ ạ̉nsy̱ klạmk</lyrics>
